Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之极！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能完完全全把1000个项目遵守下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
